  "subject": "(WIP) Register with MSB once fully launched",
  "commit_message": "(WIP) Register with MSB once fully launched\n\n/!\\ FOR PREVIEW PURPOSE ONLY /!\\\n\nTesting guide:\n\n  1. Build the jar\n      `mvn clean package`\n  2. Launch the MSB stack\n      `docker-compose -f docker-compose.msb.yml up msb_consul msb_discovery msb_apigateway`\n  3. Launch 3 NBI instances and the rest of the stack\n      `docker-compose -f docker-compose.msb.yml up --build --scale nbi=3 nbi`\n  4. By calling the endpoint http://localhost/api/microservices/v1/services,\n     verify that the NBI service has been registered with 3 nodes (status=PASSING)\n  5. By calling the endpoint http://localhost/api/nbi/v1/status,\n     verify that it is load balanced\n  6. Scale down the nbi service, 1 node will be killed\n      `docker-compose -f docker-compose.msb.yml scale nbi=2`\n  7. Verify that the dead node's status is now CRITICAL\n\nChange-Id: I2169e7b0686e60bbe4e9eba69d4b3f72411217d2\nIssue-ID: EXTAPI-90\nSigned-off-by: Quoc Nghia Nguyen <quocnghia.nguyen@orange.com>\n",
